 The mitochondria have the complete proteosynthetic apparatus, which synthesizes 
only certain mitochondrial proteins and is similar to the apparatus of the prokaryotic cell. 
Similarly as it is in bacteria, they contain 70S ribosomes (30S + 50S subunits). More than 



